subject: Olympic Games
Wrestling
lead_paragraph: Katie Downing knocked off the two-time world champion Kristie Marano in the semifinals of the United States national wrestling championships. Marano, a nine-time world wrestling medalist, still qualified for the Olympic trials in June. Marano lost her 158 ½-pound semifinal match, 1-0, 1-0.
